1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,040
I've tried looking at the time, but every clock I look at is still frozen in place,

2
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:07,080
yet time still moves.

3
00:00:07,080 --> 00:00:11,520
It's been dark outside far longer than it should be, at least I think it has.

4
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:15,800
I think what scares me the most is the fact that all doors and windows are still locked

5
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,440
and nailed shut.

6
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:19,680
As I said, I've searched all over.

7
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:22,320
Nothing, so where did those things go?

8
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:26,280
I'm not sure if this is some sort of trick or if they're hoping I'd gain a full sense

9
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,800
of optimism.

10
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:33,640
Unfortunately for them, as long as they still exist and I draw breath, they won't escape.

11
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:37,320
They took my wife from me, but they won't take anyone else.

12
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:39,560
The only place I haven't checked is the attic.
